<h1>About Farouq's Record Shop</h1>

<p>Welcome to Farouq's Record Shop, founded with a passion for music and a love of vinyl.</p>

<p>We started as a small collection of hand-picked albums spanning Hip-Hop, R&B, Pop and everything in between. Our mission is simple — to bring great music to great people.</p>

<p>Whether you're a seasoned collector or just discovering the joy of physical music, we have something for everyone. Browse our collection, find your next favourite record, and enjoy the music.</p>